bilingual.source: We need less money to complete this project.
bilingual.target: 我们需要较少的钱来完成这个项目。

bilingual.source: He prefers matcha over coffee because it has less caffeine.
bilingual.target: 他更喜欢抹茶而不是咖啡，因为它含有较少的咖啡因。

bilingual.source: Many people choose margarine because it contains less saturated fat.
bilingual.target: 许多人选择人造黄油因为它含有较少的饱和脂肪。
人们总是做较少的工作。
简化的软件意味着较少的支持.
简单的设计等同于较少的布局。

bilingual.source: You waste less time when you do this.
bilingual.target: 你这样做的话你就会花费较少的时间。
种植马铃薯需要较少的劳动力。

bilingual.source: Fewer workdays off means less catching up.
bilingual.target: 较少的工作时间假期，便等于更少的赶工。

list.abstract: less，是江南布衣旗下高端女性服饰品牌，于2003年创立。 产品包括2023春夏系列臻金新生、2022秋冬系列生命的奥德赛。 less的品牌代言人为周迅。
Less是一家共享出行服务公司，主要面向日常通勤者和其他有短途出行需求的人群。

yingyinNormal.en: You can afford to make less. Make less.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们不缺钱，别贪心。

yingyinNormal.en: 84,000 in less than 24 hours.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不到24小时，8.4万个。

yingyinNormal.en: That makes even less sense, I mean...
yingyinNormal.zh: 这更说不通啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Try less teeth. Close enough. Come on.
yingyinNormal.zh: 笑不露齿。差不多了。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, it is definitely less than a ballpark.
yingyinNormal.zh: 绝对比一个“棒球场”少。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe there's someplace that's less dangerous.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许有一个地方不是那么危险。

yingyinNormal.en: Indeed, much more rational, but rather less like a ball.
yingyinNormal.zh: 确实，聊天更理性，但是跟舞会比起来就差了点。

yingyinNormal.en: The scrutiny, the judgment. I'm partner less than a year.
yingyinNormal.zh: 监视，评判，我做合伙人还不到一年。

yingyinNormal.en: More data, more analysis, less likelihood of a terrorist attack.
yingyinNormal.zh: 数据越多，分析越全面，发生恐怖袭击的可能性就越低。

yingyinNormal.en: Less than 300 calories.
yingyinNormal.zh: 300卡路里都不到。

yingyinNormal.en: Blight does. And as it thrives, our air gets less and less oxygen.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但枯萎病菌呼吸氮气，所以当它越来越猖獗，空气里的氧气就会越来越少。

yingyinNormal.en: And therefore we expect less, and therefore indeed we get less. So what did we do?
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此我们期望的越少，得到的也就越少，所以我们该怎么办？

yingyinNormal.en: That's a lot less big. Yes, it's this much less big. I'm not even sure that's possible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那要大大减小很多啊。没错，减小的程度有这么大。我都不确定可不可行。

yingyinNormal.en: He gave me a mug. What do you think I'm drinking out of? Do you even pay attention? Honestly, less and less.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他有送我杯子。不然我在用什么喝水？你都有注意人家吗？老实说，越来越少了。

yingyinNormal.en: But even for those of us who have experienced this before, it is no less of a shock, it is no less terrifying.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但即便是那些经历过这种事的人，此事仍触目惊心，骇人听闻。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, how do you feel now? Well, I like you less.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在觉得怎样？我比较不喜欢你了。

yingyinNormal.en: It won't work. Tusk wants to help you even less than I do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没用的。塔斯克比我更不想帮你。

yingyinNormal.en: Fine, Mom. How are you? Mmm, menopausal. Now I'm less fine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 挺好，妈妈，你呢？我绝经了。现在我不怎么好了。

yingyinNormal.en: It would've been less trouble. And I might have had more fun.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这样麻烦不但少了，我还可能得到更多乐趣。

yingyinNormal.en: Our customers get exactly what they pay for, no more, no less.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的顾客们获得所有我们所承诺的东西，一样不多，一样不少。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. 较少的；次要的；条件或级别较低的；（较）小（的）

word_family.mean: adj. 等 级较低的；次要的；（little的比较级）

examination_example.sentence: Discussing the issue in private will make the powerful person feel <highlight>less</highlight> threatened.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 私下讨论这个问题会让有权势的人感觉不那么受威胁。

examination_example.sentence: Since weight loss is not my goal, it is <highlight>less</highlight> important for me to track my weight each week.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因为减肥不是我的目标，所以每周记录体重对我来说就不那么重要了。

examination_example.sentence: The consequence is that you perceive that the trip has taken <highlight>less</highlight> time than it actually has.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 结果是，你感觉这次旅行花费的时间比实际少。

examination_example.sentence: Eric Schwitzgebel's previous findings suggest that ethics professors are <highlight>less</highlight> sociable than other professors.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Eric Schwitzgebel之前的研究结果表明，伦理学教授比其他教授更不善于交际。

examination_example.sentence: Haddad and Lewis are concerned that more than half the state-government boards are <highlight>less</highlight> than 40 percent female.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Haddad和Lewis担心，超过一半的州政府董事会中，女性比例不到40%。

examination_example.sentence: It cost <highlight>less</highlight> than a fiver but she was overjoyed, and couldn't stop talking about it.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这只花了不到五英镑，但她却喜出望外，不停地谈论它。

examination_example.sentence: An isolated DNA molecule is no <highlight>less</highlight> a product of nature...than are cotton fibres that have been separated from cotton seeds.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 分离出的DNA分子就如同从棉籽上分离出来的棉纤维一样，都是自然的产物。

examination_example.sentence: Obesity is probably <highlight>less</highlight> a matter of weight than body fat.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 可能肥胖与其说是体重问题，不如说是身体脂肪问题。

examination_example.sentence: Think about how tough it is to get together 15 people, much <highlight>less</highlight> 50, who all get along perfectly.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 想想看，把15个相处融洽的人聚在一起有多难，更不用说50个了。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. 较少的；次要的；条件或级别较低的；（较）小（的）

word_family.mean: adj. 等 级较低的；次要的；（little的比较级）

examination_example.sentence: They must offer higher yields but use <highlight>less</highlight> water, nitrogen-rich fertilizers or other inputs.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们必须提供更高的产量，但使用更少的水、富氮化肥或其他投入。

examination_example.sentence: But the taxes I suggest aren't that high, <highlight>less</highlight> than 3% only.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是我建议的税率没有那么高，只有不到3%。

examination_example.sentence: The quantity of time spent together is <highlight>less</highlight> important than the content of that time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 花在一起的时间的数量不如时间的内容重要。

examination_example.sentence: Access to fashion, and the brands who police it, are becoming <highlight>less</highlight> and <highlight>less</highlight> relevant.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 接触时尚，以及管理时尚的品牌，正变得越来越无关紧要。

examination_example.sentence: Destroying old stock is a practice not just of luxury brands but of <highlight>less</highlight> prestigious fashion brands.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 销毁旧库存不仅是奢侈品牌的做法，也是不太知名的时尚品牌的做法。

examination_example.sentence: Nationality is <highlight>less</highlight> useful than socio-economic status as an indicator of one's values.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 作为个人价值观的指标，国籍不如社会经济状况有用。

sense_info_list.en: fewer in number; to a smaller degree

examination_example.sentence: A recent blog suggested maybe people are drinking <highlight>less</highlight> milk because it is poisonous to many of us.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最近的一篇博客指出，人们喝牛奶的量减少可能是因为牛奶对我们很多人来说是有毒的。

examination_example.sentence: Americans drink 37% <highlight>less</highlight> milk than they did in the 1970s.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国人喝的牛奶比20世纪70年代少了37%。

examination_example.sentence: What kind of care facility old people live in may be <highlight>less</highlight> important than we think.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 老年人住在什么样的护理场所可能没有我们想象的那么重要。

examination_example.sentence: But crucially, this was <highlight>less</highlight> so if they had completed the 30-minute jog.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但重要的是，如果他们完成了30分钟的慢跑，这种情况会减少。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Another possibility is that when there is a lot of talent on a team, some players may make <highlight>less</highlight> effort.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 另一种可能是，当一支球队中人才济济时，一些球员可能会付出更少的努力。

examination_example.sentence: In baseball, the performance of individual players is <highlight>less</highlight> dependent on teammates.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在棒球比赛中，单个球员的表现对队友的依赖性较小。

examination_example.sentence: When that happens, people become <highlight>less</highlight> likely to volunteer in the future.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当这种情况发生时，人们将来就不太可能去做志愿者了。

word_level_phrase_info.brief_definition: 不发达国家；欠发达国家

examination_example.sentence: People who forgive show <highlight>less</highlight> sadness, anger and stress and more hopefulness, according to a recent research.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 根据最近的一项研究，宽容的人表现出较少的悲伤、愤怒和压力，更多的是希望。

examination_example.sentence: People always do <highlight>less</highlight> work．
examination_example.sentence_trans: 人们总是做较少的工作。

examination_example.sentence: He was advised to eat fewer hamburgers and drink <highlight>less</highlight> cola to keep fit.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有人建议他少吃汉堡，少喝可乐来保持健康。

examination_example.sentence: So he became <highlight>less</highlight> interested in study.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 所以他对学习越来越不感兴趣。

examination_example.sentence: You weigh about 90% <highlight>less</highlight> in the pool.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你在泳池里的体重减轻了90%。

examination_example.sentence: In history, the Manchu ruled the coumtry for <highlight>less</highlight> than 200 years.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 历史上，满族统治这个国家不到200年。

examination_example.sentence: Sleeping <highlight>less</highlight> makes people more popular.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 少睡会让人更受欢迎。

examination_example.sentence: Start today, and you will find that <highlight>less</highlight> is more.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 从今天开始，你会发现少即是多。

examination_example.sentence: With the card, you can pay <highlight>less</highlight> at restaurants and shops.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你可以在餐馆和商店少付钱。

word_usage.usage:
less还是little“不多”的比较级形式。less还可以协助构成比较级，表示“更不……；较不……”。
如：I like the less colorful T-shirt.
我喜欢那件色彩不太鲜艳的T恤。
